query: SELECT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM newsletter_subscriber ns
  JOIN customer_entity ce ON ns.customer_id = ce.entity_id
  JOIN rating_option_vote rov ON ce.entity_id = rov.customer_id

    AND rov.value = 4
